+  param '8: -a <num> ; Optional: Alert if resulting file is over <num> kilobytes (default is 5000, 0 turns off)'
+  param '9: -m       ; Optional: Also create a WebM file (will one day replace GIF, Smaller and higher quality than mp4)'
